Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.93,0:24:10.65,ED-cn1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.79,0:24:14.29,ED-cn1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,love letter
